<item>
<title>女方比我收入高，我怕以后在一起有压力</title>
<link>http://www.t66y.com/htm_data/7/1801/2944332.html</link>
<guid isPermaLink="true" >http://www.t66y.com/htm_data/7/1801/2944332.html</guid>
<description>&lt;p&gt;                                         &lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;段子：女方比我收入高，我怕以后在一起有压力&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;就喜欢吹牛吹的清新脱俗的&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;                                         &lt;p align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://read.html5.qq.com/image?src=share&amp;amp;imageUrl=http://s.cimg.163.com/i/abco1.heibaimanhua.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/20180124_5a688d782fc10.jpg.0x0.auto.jpg&quot; onclick=&quot;window.open('http://www.viidii.info/?action=image&amp;amp;url=&amp;amp;src='+encodeURIComponent(this.src));&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;懂生活&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://read.html5.qq.com/image?src=share&amp;amp;imageUrl=http://s.cimg.163.com/i/abco1.heibaimanhua.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/20180124_5a688d787b5e0.jpg.0x0.auto.jpg&quot; onclick=&quot;window.open('http://www.viidii.info/?action=image&amp;amp;url=&amp;amp;src='+encodeURIComponent(this.src));&quot;/&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
